    <meta content='Adjust center values for LOA-2 through LOA5, make corresponding adjustments in AllBonesLOA5Skeletons.x3d' name='TODO'/>
    <meta content='Document how to properly adjust HAnimJoint center fields so that center of rotation is at end of each bone, not at center. Debugging with animation mode BASIC helps.' name='TODO'/>
